{"tid":1285714,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（特發）電腦技術員涉披露628警員私隱被捕 資料源自親中名校資料庫","createTime":"2019-07-04T16:16:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T16:38:31.000Z","uid":274214,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ec81ed58f51b0f2dc9bc1f655d7b5b583b4a8493","tid":1285714,"uid":274214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:16:41.000Z","msg":"反送中示威引發連串衝突及警員遭起底的爭議，警方網絡安全及科技罪案調查科接手調查後近日拘捕至少9人，其中一名被捕人，就是早前涉嫌在網上公開628名警員的私隱包括全名、手機號碼及住址，並自稱屬於國際黑客組織「匿名者（Anonymous）」的男子，他目前已獲准保釋候查，須於8月上旬向警方報到。消息稱，被捕男子是一間親中直資名校的電腦技術員，他涉嫌在學校資料庫搜尋出<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>逾628名曾為子女報讀該校的警察父母的資料</strong></span>，再於網上公開，結果他被警方查出身份。據悉警方是以他涉嫌違反《個人資料（私隱）條例》第64條拘捕他，該罪行刑罰甚重，若罪成最高可判監5年及罰款100萬。<br />\n<br />\n想洗自己啲仔女腦呀去讀親中學校<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【引渡惡法】電腦技術員涉披露628警員私隱被捕 資料源自親中名校資料庫 <br />\n <a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190704&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59789365\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190704%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59789365&d=mquyjxz0VyBhytkWBmIwRTe9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=14e6c46f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190704%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D59789365&h=bb283afb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190704&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=59789365</a>"},{"pid":"fa238a0b536e790c2a5a4ebb2a0993eaafe600e8","tid":1285714,"uid":192851,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:17:25.000Z","msg":"其實係邊間"},{"pid":"825d6af44e8ca6bfca1e0033c076b28a278ab476","tid":1285714,"uid":274214,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fa238a0b536e790c2a5a4ebb2a0993eaafe600e8","tid":1285714,"uid":192851,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:17:25.000Z","msg":"其實係邊間"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:18:42.000Z","msg":"我冇野講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}